nl.vumc.trait.oc.connect.OCConnectorException

Packages that use OCConnectorException
nl.vumc.trait.oc.connect This package supplies "low-level" connector facilities such as basic web service calls a some more aggregated methods. 
nl.vumc.trait.oc.main This package contains all main programs that can be called from the command line (see odm.sh) to perform basic operations on OpenClinica web services. 
nl.vumc.trait.oc.mirth This package contains all stuff that can be used directly from Mirth Connect Javascript. 
nl.vumc.trait.oc.odm Classes used for ODM processing and resolving.
